Cell["\<\
Of course, we\[CloseCurlyQuote]ll need to shorten the x-ranges of both graphs \
so that we can see much clearer the Moon\[CloseCurlyQuote]s orbital motion.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.985450175305099*^9, 
  3.9854502312936163`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c2ce9fac-317c-4454-b5b0-\
